21:34.544 --> 21:36.838
..tried to, by, uh...

21:37.005 --> 21:39.758
..shutting the door
in my daughter's face.

21:39.925 --> 21:44.304
I wouldn't blame you if you did
the same thing to me. I, um...

21:44.471 --> 21:46.807
Just...before
you close the door,

21:46.974 --> 21:49.184
I...I want to apologise for...

21:49.351 --> 21:52.604
..the way I treated you
the other day.

21:55.065 --> 21:59.403
And for the things that happened
over a century ago.

22:11.873 --> 22:14.751
(BUZZER BUZZES)

22:14.918 --> 22:17.796
(PARTY MUSIC)

22:29.057 --> 22:31.977
