I am a scientist.</i>

52:52.671 --> 52:56.132
<i>"I know a great deal about
the building blocks of life.</i>

52:57.300 --> 52:59.135
<i>"I know next to nothing
about...</i>

52:59.302 --> 53:01.137
<i>"..how to live it...</i>

53:03.139 --> 53:04.808
<i>"..even in part,</i>

53:04.975 --> 53:07.102
<i>"let alone in full.</i>

53:07.269 --> 53:10.105
<i>"I'm 48 years old,
and the time has come</i>

53:10.272 --> 53:12.524
<i>"for me to step into the light.</i>

53:12.691 --> 53:16.695
<i>"I know this is a journey
I must make on my own.</i>

53:16.862 --> 53:19.698
<i>"Perhaps along the way, I...</i>

53:19.865 --> 53:21.741
<i>".. will find a friend</i>

53:21.908 --> 53:24.995
<i>"who can show me where
